      validTo - String representing a expiring date in the format "YYYY-MM-DD"
      countryCode - String representing the International Direct dialing for a country
      nationalDirectDialingPrefix - String representing the National Direct Dialing prefix called within a country, between different cities or areas
      areaCode - Integer representing the area code for an area or city
      number - Long representing a telephone number
      extension - Integer representing the extention number
      physicalType - String representing the type of device such as a phone, fax, mobile, pager and so on
